Package: rdatacite
Type: Package
Title: R Client for DataCite OAI-PMH methods and RESTful API
Description: A programmatic interface to the Web Service methods provided
    by DataCite (http://datacite.org/), including functions to interface with
    OAI-PMH metadata service, and a RESTful API. The RESTful API is backed by
    SOLR, allowing expressive queries, including faceting, stats on varialbes,
    and more-like-this queries.
Version: 0.0.8.99
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Date: 2015-03-10
